'''Leslie Schofield''' (born [[December 12]], [[1930s|1938]]) is an English actor who portrayed [[Chief]] [[Moradmin Bast]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']]. Footage of Schofield cut from ''A New Hope'' was used in ''[[The Star Wars Holiday Special]]'', though Bast's death on the [[Death Star]] indicate this was [[Unidentified Moradmin Bast look-alike|a different officer]].

In [[1960s|1969]] and [[1977]], he appeared in the sci-fi series [[Wikipedia:Doctor Who|''Doctor Who'']] in the stories [[Wikipedia:The War Games|''The War Games'']] and [[Wikipedia:The Face of Evil|''The Face of Evil'']]. He has also contributed to the soap opera ''EastEnders'' and the sci-fi series ''Blake's 7''.

